cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.GR 

The paper focuses on self-supervised learning and generative adversarial networks, which are topics commonly studied in the machine learning community. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves image generation and analysis, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Additionally, the proposed multi-class minimax game involves competition and optimization, which are topics commonly studied in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper involves the analysis and improvement of GAN models, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics).
